&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Individuals in this role have a passion for technology and the ambition to dive head-first into new challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years experience working in a Sales, Customer Success, Account Management, Sales/Business Development&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
