&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead, hire, and grow a high-ownership team; roll up sleeves, ready to do deep into the trenches, by staying close to design docs and code, rather than managing from a distance. Coach engineers, level them up, and clear the friction that slows them down.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Roadmap &amp;amp; trajectory:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive the arc from today&#39;s compute toward the next-generation of compute platforms. Ground prioritization in customer and design-partner feedback, and turn ambiguous, fast-moving requirements into predictable, iterative delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
