&lt;li&gt;Experience building developer-facing products where deployment simplicity and operational excellence are key differentiators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with autoscaling systems, workload scheduling, and resource optimization at scale&lt;/li&gt;
